核心目标配置：​
• CONFIG_TARGET_qualcommax=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_qualcommax_ipq60xx=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_qualcommax_ipq60xx_DEVICE_jdcloud_re-cs-02=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_BOARD="qualcommax"
• CONFIG_TARGET_SUBTARGET="ipq60xx"
• CONFIG_TARGET_PROFILE="DEVICE_jdcloud_re-cs-02"
• CONFIG_TARGET_ARCH_PACKAGES="aarch64_cortex-a53"
默认软件包选择：​
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_mtd=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_netifd=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_nss-firmware-ipq6018=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_odhcp6c=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_odhcpd-ipv6only=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_opkg=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_ppp=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_ppp-mod-pppoe=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_procd=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_procd-ujail=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_uboot-envtools=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_uci=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_uclient-fetch=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_urandom-seed=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_urngd=y
• CONFIG_DEFAULT_wpad-openssl=y
系统与镜像配置：​
• CONFIG_TARGET_ROOTFS_INITRAMFS=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_INITRAMFS_COMPRESSION_ZSTD=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_ROOTFS_SQUASHFS=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_SQUASHFS_BLOCK_SIZE=256
• CONFIG_TARGET_UBIFS_FREE_SPACE_FIXUP=y
• CONFIG_TARGET_UBIFS_JOURNAL_SIZE=""
内核与构建选项（部分关键项）：​
• CONFIG_KERNEL_PRINTK=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_SWAP=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_DEBUG_FS=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_KALLSYMS=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_DEBUG_KERNEL=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_DEBUG_INFO=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_DEBUG_INFO_REDUCED=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_FRAME_WARN=2048
• CONFIG_KERNEL_AIO=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_IO_URING=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_CGROUPS=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_NAMESPACES=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_USER_NS=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_NET_NS=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_IPV6=y
• CONFIG_KERNEL_MPTCP=y
已选择的额外软件包：​
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_ubi-utils=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_ucode-mod-html=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_ucode-mod-lua=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_usbids=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_usbutils=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_v2dat=y

1. Docker 引擎与服务 (Docker CE)​
这是 Docker 运行的核心。
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_docker-ce=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_dockerd=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_containerd=y
2. Docker 依赖的内核模块
这些模块是 Docker 容器功能的基础，必须启用。
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-br-netfilter=y (用于桥接网络的 Netfilter)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-dax=y (直接访问存储)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-dm=y (设备映射器)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-dummy=y (虚拟网络接口)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-fs-btrfs=y (Btrfs 文件系统支持，用于存储驱动)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-ikconfig=y (允许从 /proc 访问内核配置)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-ip6tables=y (IPv6 防火墙)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-ipt-extra=y (额外的 iptables 匹配模块)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-ipt-raw=y (RAW 表支持，已存在于您的清单中)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-ipt-tproxy=y (透明代理支持)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-iptables=y(Netfilter iptables 核心)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-nat=y (网络地址转换)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-conntrack=y (连接跟踪)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-conntrack-netlink=y(连接跟踪的用户空间通信)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-conntrack6=y (IPv6 连接跟踪)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-nat6=y (IPv6 NAT)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-reject=y (连接拒绝)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nf-reject6=y (IPv6 连接拒绝)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nfnetlink=y (Netfilter 用户空间通信)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nft-bridge=y(nftables 桥接支持)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nft-core=y (nftables 核心)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nft-nat=y (nftables NAT)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nft-netdev=y(nftables 网络设备)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-nft-offload=y(nftables 硬件卸载)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-veth=y (虚拟以太网设备，用于容器网络)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-vxlan=y (VXLAN 隧道，用于 overlay 网络)
3. Dockerman 图形界面 (LuCI App)​
这是您提到的管理界面。
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-dockerman=y
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-i18n-dockerman-zh-cn=y(中文语言包，可选但推荐)
4. 其他可能需要的工具
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_libnetwork=y (Docker 网络库)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_tini=y (容器初始化系统，Docker 推荐)
• CONFIG_PACKAGE_docker-compose=y (如果您需要 Docker Compose，可选)
